entry.title: Russian Shelling Forces Ukraine Nuclear Plant to Run on Backup Generators
entry.content: Moscow resumed attacks on energy infrastructure overnight and Kyiv said the Zaporizhzhia nuclear-power facility had 15 days’ worth of fuel left to run generators.

entry.title: Who Is China's New No. 2? A Business Pragmatist or a Party Loyalist?
entry.content: Li Qiang’s record suggests he could serve as a moderating influence on Xi Jinping, but he has also fallen in line when it mattered.
